                        </h6>
                        <p class="fontmdsize" id="id56">We faced a task of involving new partners and customers into German B2C ecommerce platform. SEO optimization was implemented in the core of Drupal-powered website, as well as PayPal mass payment system. Our UI designers delivered new responsive design, ensuring the application is smoothly displayed both on PCs and touch-first devices. The application became convenient for content publishing and advertising.
