                        <h6 id="id51">Drupal, migration, backend</h6>
                        <p class="fontmdsize" id="id57">Our task was migrating the web-portal under development on Drupal 7. We delivered several access roles for different types of users, faceted search, Citrix webinars and livestreams, implemented rating system, user notifications, Google maps and Memcache integration. Drupal has covered the requirements of SEO optimization, registration process and content management. The application was tested under load, as long as it was promoted during the development process.

