                        <p class="fontmdsize" id="id58">We constructed a multilingual website for Stuttgart marketing agency using Drupal 8 technology. Perspectivas is a German exchanging platform that sells services of recruiting employees abroad Germany, their adaptation and relocation, while the English version engages foreign job seekers. Backend requirements were content management, blog section, media library and FAQ; also we delivered frontend part to provide intuitive and stylish UI/UX.
